1) Copy Selection to Clipboard:
-----------------------------------
Preferences -> General -> Clipboard -> Automatically copy selection to keyboard
Select the Text -> It will be copied
Press 'Ctrl + Shift + v' to Insert

2) Font Size and Appearance:
--------------------------------
Preferences -> Appearance -> Increase font size to 12
Uncheck -> Allow Bold Text
Uncheck-> Display menubar in New Windows
Check -> Use custom styling to make tabs slim




Keyboard Shortcut to close tab
